thread.title: Howie

author: Howie
title: Howie
text: Overall, good value and quick shipping. Before installing, used to be you had to pull a small paper tab. Now I noticed there's the usual tab but also another piece of tap. I thought that had to be removed but it wouldn't come off so easily. I did contact customer service and was told that you don't have to remove it. Maybe a note on the packaging is in order? Good product though.
